message.content: cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR. The paper deals with the task of Visual Question Answering (VQA), which involves understanding both visual and textual information. This task is closely related to computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses deep learning models (cs.LG) and their behavior analysis (cs.IR).
